<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About KASH</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&family=Droid+Serif:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Import fonts */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&family=Droid+Serif:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #fef7ed;
            color: #333;
            font-family: 'Droid Serif', serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        /* Typography */
        h1, h3 {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        .page-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af, #3b82f6);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .page-header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            margin: 0;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            padding-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        /* Card Grid Layout */
        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        /* Individual Card Styling */
        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #f97316; /* Orange icon */
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        .card p {
            flex-grow: 1; /* Pushes the button to the bottom */
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .card a {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #1e40af;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            align-self: flex-start; /* Align button to the left */
        }

        .card a:hover {
            background-color: #1c3d90;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }
            .page-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .page-header {
                padding: 3rem 0;
                margin-bottom: 3rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
     <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    <header class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About KASH</h1>
            <p>Learn more about our organization, our people, and our principles.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="card-grid">

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div>
                    <h3>About KASH Logo</h3>
                    <p>Discover the story and symbolism behind the KASH logo and its meaning.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/AboutKASH_Logo">Read More</a>
                </div>
              
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i></div>
                    <h3>Who We Are</h3>
                    <p>Explore the journey, history, and impact of the KASH organization.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/AboutUs">Read More</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
                    <h3>Vision & Mission</h3>
                    <p>Understand the core vision and mission that drives the KASH initiative.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/Vision_Mission">Read More</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-handshake-angle"></i></div>
                    <h3>About SOLID</h3>
                    <p>Learn about our parent organization, Solidarity for Developing Communities.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/AboutSOLID_KASH">Read More</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i></div>
                    <h3>Principal's Desk</h3>
                    <p>A message from the Principal highlighting our goals, achievements, and vision.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/PrincipalsDesk">Read More</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i></div>
                    <h3>Faculty</h3>
                    <p>Meet our dedicated and experienced faculty members behind our success.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/Faculty">Read More</a>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-landmark"></i></div>
                    <h3>Board Members</h3>
                    <p>Get to know the guiding members of our Executive Management Board.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/Government">Read More</a>
                </div>
        
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-users-cog"></i></div>
                    <h3>KASH Executive</h3>
                    <p>Get introduced to the KASH executive team and their leadership roles.</p>
                    <a href="/WhoWeAre/KASH_Executive">Read More</a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
</body>
</html>